      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-300 mb-8">
        English has a peculiar aversion to ending words with V. While hundreds of words contain V in the middle or beginning, the number that actually terminate in V is shockingly small. For Scrabble players, this rarity creates both a challenge (how do you dump a V tile late?) and an opportunity (V-endings are nearly impossible for opponents to hook). Here is every valid V-ending word you need to know.
