      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">Strategy for V-Ending Hooks</h2>

      <p>V-ending words are defensively powerful because they are nearly impossible to extend. Most V-ending words cannot take an S hook, and very few front hooks work either. Use this to your advantage.</p>

      <div class="not-prose my-6 grid grid-cols-1 gap-4">
