        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-purple-400 transition-colors">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">Quick V dump in endgame:</span> If you are stuck with V late in the game, REV, DEV, GOV, and LUV all use common letters (R, E, D, G, O, L, U). You will almost always have the companion letter to offload V.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-purple-400 transition-colors">
